1212 Fifth Ave., at the S.E. corner of 102nd Street.
About 1925.

709204f-a.text:
Fifth Avenue, looking north from between 102nd and 103rd Streets, in Central Park, showing the New York Academy of Medicine, the site for the Museum of the City of New York; the Heckscher Foundation for children, and the Fifth Avenue Hospital.
May 15, 1928.
P.L.Sperr, Photographer.
